# {{lb|en|grammar}} A non-[[finite]] verb form considered [[neutral]] with respect to inflection; depending on language variously found used with [[auxiliary verb]]s, in [[subordinate clause]]s, or acting as a [[gerund]], and often as the [[dictionary form]].
# {{lb|en|grammar}} A [[verbal noun]] formed from the infinitive of a verb.

